          },
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Flag evals + conversions (traces)",
      "description": "POST /api/orders traces. Each order span carries the feature_flag.evaluation and feature_flag.track span events together: open a row to see the evaluation (the variant) and the conversion correlated on one trace.",
